\b 4.2 Qualitative Evaluation\par
\b0\par
This section explains the comparative performance of the three enhancement models on the EUVP dataset using the results summarized in the evaluation table. The table includes both no-reference and reference-based metrics, allowing the performance of the models to be assessed from different perspectives.\par
\par
